recommendation.new_prompt_text:
Identify exactly two distinct, actionable algorithmic components required to solve this problem. 

Each component must be a specific computational task (e.g., a state-update rule, a search procedure, or a scoring function) rather than a high-level strategy or conceptual summary. Do not exceed 2 helpers. Do not restate the original question. Use plain text only inside helper instructions (no markdown, code fences, or LaTeX).

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    },
    {
      "label": "helper_2",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the second helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}
